column3: Traffic Alert for N Cleveland Rd:
column4: Access to N Cleveland Rd from Winchester Rd toward I-64 is shut down due to an asphalt truck on its side near I-64.
Inbound Newtown Pike at Nandino Blvd
column5: A semi and an SUV are involved.  The semi is in a ditch.  Inbound Newtown Pike traffic diverted to Nandino Blvd.
Two separate collisions reported.  Significant traffic impact in this area.
